snippet.title: Official Contraption Maker Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Now available on Steam Early Access! http://store.steampowered.com/app/241240

Contraption Maker is the spiritual successor to the classic puzzle game The Incredible Machine. Stay updated on the game by subscribing to this channel or checking out the devlog: http://blog.contraptionmaker.com/
